high_descs: Turn around then walk straight turn right on the toilet
Pick up the candle in front of spray bottle on the tank
Turn right move slightly on the sink counter
Put the candle in front of the left side of the sink
Move slightly on your right facing down on the cabinet
Open the cabinet pick up the candle then close the cabinet
Turn left move slightly forward then turn right facing the counter
Put the candle at the back of the first candle
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on the edge of the sink

high_descs: Turn around, proceed to wall, turn right, proceed to counter.
Pick up candle from counter, located to the right of the pink soap.
Turn right then left to position self closer to sink area of counter.
Place candle on counter, directly below and to the left corner of the sink.
Turn right, then left to position self directly in front of sink.
Open left cabinet below sink.  Remove candle stick from the shelf in the cabinet, located on the right hand side.
Turn left then right to position self directly in front of pump bottle on counter.
Place candle on counter directly in front of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles to the counter.

high_descs: Move to the back of the toilet where the yellow tube is on the toilet tank
Pick up the yellow tube on the toilet tank
Carry the yellow tube over to the left side of the bathroom counter top
Place the tube on the left counter top in front of the sink
Face the bottom left cabinet on the left side under the sink
Open the bottom left cabinet under the sink and remove the yellow tube in the cabinet, close cabinet
Carry the yellow tube to the bathroom counter top
Place the yellow tube on the counter in front of the sink next to the other yellow tube
anns.task_desc: Place two yellow tubes on the bathroom counter top
